_sText:
Hi gamers!

This is my first orange map (or dev map, as you want).

So, it's a little castle and you have to kill the other team (that's the point of the game, right?)
You can go to the other respawn zone by walking or swimming.
It's a 24 slots map, 12 Ts and 12 CTs.

Oh, and by the way, sorry for my bad english.

Enjoy!
